#--------------------------------------------
# README file for the cfeditor project on xtext
# author: Andreas Bender
# E-mail:andreas.bender@kit.edu
#--------------------------------------------

Import project into eclipse:

Download: Eclipse Helios for RCP and RAP Developers (http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/packages/eclipse-rcp-and-rap-developers/heliosr)
Install Xtext from: http://www.eclipse.org/modeling/tmf/downloads/?project=xtext

OR

Download full Helios Xtext Distribution (recommended) from: http://xtext.itemis.com/xtext/language=en/23947/downloads

In eclipse: 
-	File->Import
-	Select “Existing Projects into Workspace”
-	Next “Select root directory:” Browse…->Select folder: “cfeditorxtext”
-	Finish

Run project: Right click on org.eclipse.xtext.cfeditor (project folder) -> Run As -> Eclipse Application
